---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="포트폴리오" currentPath="/portfolio">
  <!-- 포트폴리오 헤더 -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 py-16">
    <div class="container-max">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">포트폴리오</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">HelfLab이 완료한 주요 프로젝트들을 소개합니다</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 프로젝트 갤러리 -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6].map((i) => (
          <div class="group overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-indigo-400 h-48 relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-white">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">프로젝트 {i}</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">이 프로젝트는 고객의 비즈니스 요구사항을 충족시키는 혁신적인 솔루션입니다.</p>
              <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded">React</span>
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded">TypeScript</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded">AWS</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- 프로젝트 상세 -->
      <div class="mt-16 pt-16 border-t">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12">주요 프로젝트 소개</h2>
        
        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517694712202-14dd9538aa97?w=500&h=300&fit=crop" alt="프로젝트" class="rounded-lg" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">E-Commerce 플랫폼</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">풀 스택 e커머스 솔루션으로 실시간 재고 관리, 결제 시스템, 배송 추적 기능을 포함합니다.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4">
                <li>150% 매출 증가</li>
                <li>99.9% 가용성</li>
                <li>50만+ 월간 사용자</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">Next.js</span>
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">Node.js</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">실시간 분석 대시보드</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">기업의 실시간 데이터를 시각화하는 고성능 분석 대시보드입니다.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4">
                <li>밀리초 단위의 데이터 갱신</li>
                <li>직관적인 UI/UX</li>
                <li>1000+ 동시 사용자 지원</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">React</span>
                <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">WebSocket</span>
                <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded">Redis</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=500&h=300&fit=crop" alt="분석 대시보드" class="rounded-lg" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 통계 -->
  <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container-max">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">50+</div>
          <p class="text-blue-100">완료된 프로젝트</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">100+</div>
          <p class="text-blue-100">만족한 고객</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">500+</div>
          <p class="text-blue-100">개발 시간</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">99.9%</div>
          <p class="text-blue-100">가용성</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
